#: .\website\templates\about.html:11 .\website\templates\mobile_about.html:11
msgid ""
"OWASP Bug Logging Tool (BLT) - A gamified crowd-sourced QA testing and "
"vulnerability disclosure platform for websites, apps, git repositories, and "
"more"
msgstr ""

#: .\website\templates\about.html:20 .\website\templates\mobile_about.html:20
msgid ""
"Learn about BLT - The gamified crowd-sourced QA testing and vulnerability "
"disclosure platform with AI-powered tools for efficient testing and "
"development"
msgstr ""

#: .\website\templates\about.html:31 .\website\templates\mobile_about.html:28
msgid "About"
msgstr "के बारे में"

#: .\website\templates\about.html:35 .\website\templates\mobile_about.html:31
#, python-format
msgid ""
"is a 100%% free to use, open-source, non-commercial and non-profit gamified "
"crowd-sourced QA testing and vulnerability disclosure platform."
msgstr ""

#: .\website\templates\about.html:38 .\website\templates\mobile_about.html:34
msgid ""
"We help coders and security researchers discover organizations, "
"repositories, and projects to test and report to, making it easier to find "
"meaningful security work and contribute to the community."
msgstr ""

#: .\website\templates\about.html:41 .\website\templates\mobile_about.html:37
msgid ""
"We support testing across websites, apps, git repositories, and other "
"projects. Our team has created dozens of open-source tools and embraces AI-"
"powered processes for efficient testing and development."
msgstr ""

#: .\website\templates\about.html:43 .\website\templates\mobile_about.html:39
msgid ""
"Every reward goes directly to the testers and security researchers who find "
"and report issues."
msgstr ""

#: .\website\templates\about.html:53 .\website\templates\mobile_about.html:45
msgid "Our Mission"
msgstr ""

#: .\website\templates\about.html:56
msgid ""
"To create a secure digital environment through gamified crowd-sourced "
"testing. From websites and apps to git repositories and projects, we believe "
"every digital platform should be thoroughly tested and secure. We leverage "
"AI and open-source tools to make quality assurance accessible and rewarding "
"for everyone."
msgstr ""

#: .\website\templates\about.html:64 .\website\templates\mobile_about.html:51
msgid "What We Do"
msgstr ""

#: .\website\templates\about.html:67
msgid ""
"BLT provides a comprehensive gamified platform for crowd-sourced QA testing "
"and vulnerability disclosure across websites, apps, git repositories, and "
"projects. We've developed dozens of open-source tools and AI-powered "
"features to enhance testing efficiency and collaboration."
msgstr ""

